J. Del Pozo In White Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.1875

White sands drift along in the wind as her feet savor every moment of the heated roughness against her soft toes. The delicate elegance of her persona shines through her quiet graceful demeanor as the soothing waves of J. Del Pozo In White caress her skin. The luxury fragrance takes inspiration from creamy white pearls and redefines the sensuality of a woman. Maintaining the delicate balance between nature and the woman the Eau de Toilette swathes you in an incomparable yet simple elegance. The gossamery balance created by the union of several exotic elements caresses your skin with pure seduction.

2007 saw the creation of In White from the celebrated house of Jesus Del Pozo by famed perfumers Francis Kurkdjin and Vioaline David. Bergamot bamboo leaf and lemon blossom create fresh green opening notes even as the heart holds a storm of passion created by orchid orange blossoms magnolia almond blossoms white freesia and jasmine. The redolent white flowers give way to iris flower and deep powdery musk leaving the dry down to induce memories of a beautiful night spent by the lake. Designed by Juan Gatti the pearl shaped bottle that contains the dainty fragrance is a serene soft poetic representation of the wholesome female form. Rejoice in the luminescent prism of fragrance that In White creates.

J. Del Pozo Duende Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.1800

Ethereal and unique this luxury scent from the established house of Jesus Del Pozo embodies the verbally indescribable Spanish concept that is shrouded with intrigue. J. Del Pozo Duende marries an array of radiant natural extracts and transforms the wonderfully carefree woman into a mystical nymph. A magical Eau de Toilette created by Olivier Cresp it holds within its aura a sensual charm and divine appeal.

The top note cuddles together sweet bergamot bright hints of tangerine ripe scent of melon and bittersweet lime giving you a refreshing aroma. Following this is the heart note that enfolds exotic jasmine intensely sweet ylang-ylang along with subtle and clean notes of mimosa. Finishing off with a deeper base note of distinct sandalwood woody notes of cedar warm wormwood tied together with the herbal and graceful allure of thyme. Composed of vibrant and aromatic ingredients this fresh floral woody fragrance adds a sprinkle of rustic charm to dull city mornings. Delicately carved the glass bottle that encases this fragrance conjures up the image of a simple drop of water - pure and untainted. Offsetting the simple structure the top takes on a grand gesture with an elongated and feminine twist. A whiff of this perfume and sink into the soul of the profound yet obscure Duende.

Fruity and floral Halloween Kiss Sexy from the Spanish fashion house of Jesus Del Pozo is the definition of sensual femininity. Sweet and sensual Halloween Kiss Sexy was created by perfumer Christophe Raynaud as an emblem for the cosmopolitan woman who is unafraid to express herself without taking recourse to false modesty. Like pink flowers wrapped in velvety creamy caramel this luxurious Eau de Toilette lifts your spirits and enshrouds you in a cloud of flowery refreshing essences reminiscent of a spring-time romance.

Invigorating like a passionate first embrace the refreshing top note of Halloween Kiss Sexy opens with green apple lemon and peach juice. The floral heart of peony freesia and cyclamen add a refreshing sweetness to the fragrance and trail into a warm heady base note of sandalwood and velvety musk. Like the yin to Halloween's yang Halloween Kiss Sexy is for a woman who takes charge. Not for her the role of a victim she is the perpetrator fearless and uninhibited.

J. Del Pozo Halloween Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.1853

Eccentric yet thrilling this luxury scent accentuates the woman who personifies the bewildering duality of seduction and innocence. For the bewitching woman J.Del Pozo Halloween celebrates her playful yet dark streak. Created by perfumer Max Gavarry of IFF this entrancing Eau de Toilette is made for the eponymous house of J.Del Pozo.

Piquing your interest from the first waft the top note packs a killer combination of powdery soft hints of violet earthy and refreshing green banana that is garnished with bright citrusy notes of green lime along with the refreshing and soothing essence of Alaskan seas. Evaporating into the heart you are wrapped in a haze of lush and lemony magnolia exotic hints of muguet spicy notes of pepper delicate tuberose with traces of atrezzo violet. It descends into a warm base note of rich sandalwood aromatic notes of incense creamy vanilla and resinous myrrh. An array of aromatic ingredients fuse together to produce an intoxicating floral oriental fragrance. With a spritz of this hypnotic perfume transform your evenings into a carnival of whimsy and fancy. Poured into a crystal amphora bottle this sensuous fragrance radiates a lovely shade of lavender. A silver aluminium base and top complete the mesmerising vial. Walk into the masquerade as the ravishing sorceress in an ethereal aura who has cast her spell on the night.
